attributes.additional_details: Our English UK children should never be with out health care. If there is no funding then stop putting up these imagrants that cost tax people's money and not let our children and the contries future suffer
attributes.background: I am unable to get my 5 year and 2 year old on NHS dentist and it is beyond a joke. Iam being to by the dentist that there is no funding for this. I have worked from the age of 15 and have been a tax payer since. But people get it to the UK and get everything paid for them
